data.description: SELLER CONCESSIONS FOR RATE BUY DOWN OR TO KEEP IN YOUR BANK WITH ACCEPT OFFER.  This Beautiful 2-bedroom home is nestled in the heart of Lakeland’s desirable COUNTRY CLUB ESTATES neighborhood.
